1.0.name: wordpress/dovie
1.0.description: The Dovie plugin allows you to easily add videos and channels from your Dovie account to your Wordpress posts. You can view all your videos and channels from inside your Wordpress account. Click the one you want to add and the Dovie plugin will insert the necessary code for you automatically.
